title: 15 Pack 4.7" Matte Black Cabinet Pulls, Modern Concealed Pulls with Finger Edge Design, Suitable for Kitchen and Wardrobe, Stylish Tab Handle for Drawers and Cabinets
description: Elevate the look of your cabinets and furniture with this set of 20 Aandxmok cabinet handles and edge pulls. Crafted from durable aluminum alloy, these hidden pulls offer a sleek and modern design that seamlessly blends into any decor. With their sturdy construction and smooth finish, they provide a secure grip while adding a touch of elegance to your space. Easily install these handles on kitchen cabinets, bathroom vanities, or any other furniture piece for a stylish and functional upgrade. Measuring approximately 4 inches (10.16 cm) in length, they offer a comfortable grip and complement both traditional and contemporary styles. Enhance the aesthetic appeal of your home with this versatile set of cabinet handles and edge pulls.
